This can affect any project which uses {{magefile.go}} under {{.mage}} subdirectory.

Commit msg: {{JI-2019 fix compatibility with Go 1.16}}

Running these commands to migrate/fix:

{noformat}git checkout master
git pull
git mv .mage magebuild
sed -i "s/\.mage/magebuild/g" Makefile
git add Makefile
# check it…
git commit -m "JI-2019 fix compatibility with Go 1.16"
git push{noformat}

